<p>just to let you know &#8211; I made these using half the cream stated for the ganaches and the consistency was perfect in both. The brownies are absolutely delicious and they look great. Also, I made them in a 9&#8243; square pan and divided the recipe by two-thirds which works perfectly. 1&#8243; brownies are great, as they&#8217;re quite rich. Just heading to the kitchen now to make another batch for my friend&#8217;s birthday, no doubt they&#8217;ll be much appreciated! Thanks for the recipe, I know I&#8217;ll get a lot of use out of it!</p>
<p>Bell</p>
